            "body": "I appreciate that the requirement is documented, and I in fact remember reading it. However, I still felt that the `git` requirement was surprisingly strict _in practice_, since it required me to install a newer `git` on a not that old OS.\n\nThis issue is mostly meant to raise awareness. I _suspect_ that the git requirement might be surprising to other users as well. I can't speak to how big the performance gain of `--also-filter-submodules` is, and even less so how this compares to compatiblity/ease of use concerns.",
            "created_at": "2025-11-13T21:18:06Z",
